{
  "text": "For each AOI, we obtained the Visual Attention (VA) Index that takes into account the percentage of total fixation duration (%TFD) for the selected AOI and the percentage of the area itself (%Area), calculated as in [CITATION_1] :",
  "correct_citation": {
